This paper deals with the problem of boosting for regression in the online learning setting. The paper discusses the use of weak and strong learning algorithms and their relationship with a base class of regression functions. The paper also introduces an online gradient boosting algorithm. Given the focus on machine learning algorithms and regression, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
